        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[In the latest 1.11 version, we are excited to announce the release of the Streaming API.]]></summary>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<div class="container_pLOk"><img src="https://promptpal.github.io/assets/images/logo-6a9d31d05fe1069d8c397ca17a9a393c.png" alt="promptpal logo" class="logo_HRaL"><div><h2 class="version_xk68">PromptPal <!-- -->1.11</h2><ul class="features_AgtB"><li class="raycast-tag feature_cEYN featureText_il9a">Streaming</li><li class="raycast-tag feature_cEYN featureText_il9a">Types</li></ul></div></div>
<p>In the latest 1.11 version, we are excited to announce the release of the Streaming API.</p>
<p>with the latest <a href="https://jsr.io/@prompt-pal/node-sdk" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">JavaScript SDK</a> and <a href="https://github.com/PromptPal/go-sdk" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Golang SDK</a> you can now use the streaming API to get responses faster than ever before.</p>
